{"tid":2035932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何鴻燊係共匪頭馬，佢憑咩俾人悼念！","createTime":"2020-05-26T07:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T07:52:46.000Z","uid":277916,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de42e8e8dc4dbceca15a6ecc087c94f4444a280c","tid":2035932,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢害到幾多人家破人亡<br />\n賭仔唔去佢度賭就去第二度<br />\n但佢一家都係紅底<br />\n個仔娶支那人<br />\n仲有北韓唯一一個賭場都係佢開架<br />\n同支共無關係你估佢點開？<br />\n去含金正日咩唔通<br />\n醒下啦<br />\n呢條仆街根本就係支共嘅白手套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要悼念就悼念麥理浩<br />\n甚至更加應該悼念李鵬飛<br />\n佢喺香港主權移交嗰陣同鄧蓮如爵士出咗咁多力<br />\n無佢就唔會有一國兩制<br />\n悼念佢唔係更加反映到一國兩制已死嘅命題咩？"},{"pid":"77718279d659985f3135e610551b34a8280cc583","tid":2035932,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"自推開始<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d387f548e1db1f77d0ba7a6c8595c40084e9c820","tid":2035932,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"P牌好難推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我上去！！！"},{"pid":"689ca9038c17070904759a73be95d02d4d2b0170","tid":2035932,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />